<br>Contact us today for more information about the compliance management solutions we offer for health and social care organisations.<br>
<br><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/pages/complyplus-cqc-compliance-system" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(0, 71, 178);"><i>ComplyPlus</i></span></a> software has proven effective for many providers, and we wish to assist others so they may also benefit from it.<br>
</span></p><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ggpkNl jdwwxc pf-183_ pf-heading-1-h3 _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fThTNe cAYhcc pf-185_">Conclusion</span></h2><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/are-you-ready-for-the-cqc-single-assessment-framework--conclusion--dr-richard-dune--1677672351476.jpg?v=1677672366" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/are-you-ready-for-the-cqc-single-assessment-framework--conclusion--dr-richard-dune--1677672351476.jpg?v=1677672366 1536w" width="4000" height="2644" alt="Are you ready for the CQC single assessment framework? - Conclusion - Dr Richard Dune -" title="Are you ready for the CQC single assessment framework - Conclusion - Dr Richard Dune -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-sLtfs jkHPMQ pf-186_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-lnPyOc exfzrW pf-187_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fThTNe cAYhcc pf-189_">Despite the substantial changes, the CQC's primary objective is to improve the quality of health and social care services in the UK. To achieve this goal, they are shifting their focus to place a stronger emphasis on assessment over inspection and conduct more continuous assessments based on evidence.
<br><br>By continuously assessing service providers, the CQC will be able to determine if it is achieving its aims. As a result, providers can identify what needs improvement and take appropriate measures.
